---
title: Southwest Beef Salad with Corn and Creamy Lime Dressing
description: Southwest spice flavours tender beef and quick-cooking corn in this speedy salad. Want to make it even faster? Leave the tomatoes whole!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwest-turkey-salad-5055740a-3919cd9a.jpg
